{"tid":1809586,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國承認空襲伊拉克巴格達機場　以阻伊朗襲擊圖謀","createTime":"2020-01-03T08:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T08:28:29.000Z","uid":56533,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ccb672d097dcf504fdd4dff7b3bf0dfa32022b3","tid":1809586,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1500816_1_20200103125848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1500816_1_20200103125848.jpg&h=a3c8713c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊拉克首都巴格達國際機場遇襲，最少8人死亡，包括當地伊朗勢力的將領，及被指與伊朗關係密切的伊拉克什葉派民兵組織「人民動員」一名副指揮官。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部說總統特朗普下令發動空襲，又說是要阻止伊朗日後的襲擊圖謀。國防部指出，被殺的伊朗革命衛隊將領蘇萊馬尼，一直積極策劃針對區內美國外交人員的行動，亦與伊拉克民眾日前破壞駐巴格達美國大使館事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n美軍早前空襲伊拉克及敘利亞境內的伊朗什葉派武裝組織「真主旅」據點，巴格達大批民眾不滿，除夕當日衝擊當地美國大使館。美國國防部長埃斯珀早前已揚言採取必要措施，保障美國人員及利益，又指伊拉克政府無足夠行動，阻止伊朗施襲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500816-20200103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500816-20200103.htm&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7AaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=a588ed53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500816-20200103.htm&h=3c47d600\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500816-20200103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a5ffc5523c0cebcf827a568dbf33b41a71039c3c","tid":1809586,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"班加西13小時？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca8e95dc2700d2f64b834883ade2801532da22e","tid":1809586,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ffc5523c0cebcf827a568dbf33b41a71039c3c","tid":1809586,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T08:23